OL,3,CFarmer recalls emotional and financial
OL,4,Ctoll of losing sheep in dog attacks
OL,6,FA farmer has told UTV that the
OL,7,Femotional toll of losing sheep in dog
OL,8,Fattacks is worse than the financial
OL,9,Fimpact.
OL,11,FThat's despite the price farmers paid
OL,12,Ffor losing livestock and dealing with
OL,13,Finjured animals jumping by nearly half
OL,14,Fin 2024 compared to the previous year.
OL,16,FFarm animals in Northern Ireland worth
OL,17,Fan estimated #218,000 were severely
OL,18,Finjured or killed in dog attacks in
OL,19,F2024, according to NFU Mutual. In
OL,20,F2023, the figure was #147,000, an
OL,21,Fincrease of 48%.
