OL,3,CFarmer recalls emotional and financial
OL,4,Ctoll of losing sheep in dog attacks
OL,6,FThe overall UK figure actually dropped
OL,7,Fby 26%, costing farmers #1.8m.
OL,9,FWilliam Beattie tends to cattle and
OL,10,Fsheep in rural Ballymoney.
OL,12,FIn January, a dog chased 50 sheep
OL,13,Fclose to his farm, cornering three of
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,FHe told UTV: "It (the dog) cut one
OL,17,Fanimal quite badly all down the sides
OL,18,Fof the neck and down the sides of the
OL,19,Fleg. That animal needed immediate
OL,20,Fveterinary assistance, just for
OL,21,Fantibiotics and pain relief."
