OL,6,FSadly, the sheep lived for two days
OL,7,Fbefore dying.
OL,9,F"The emotional stress, I would nearly
OL,10,Fput as being worse," added William.
OL,12,F"There was one occasion on a Sunday
OL,13,Fmorning two years ago when I went to
OL,14,Fjust check some sheep down the road...
OL,15,Fand a dog overnight had attacked them
OL,16,Fand just totally gutted them.
