OL,3,CFarmer recalls emotional and financial
OL,4,Ctoll of losing sheep in dog attacks
OL,6,F"It's very traumatic to come across
OL,7,Fthat. It just leaves a trail of blood
OL,8,Fafterwards and then it's the after
OL,9,Fthat are left behind distressed, and
OL,10,Fthey never get over the stress."
OL,12,FHannah Binns, NFU Mutual's Rural
OL,13,FAffairs Specialist, said: "It is
OL,14,Fworrying to see the estimated cost of
OL,15,Flivestock worrying rise in Northern
OL,16,FIreland last year, especially at a
OL,17,Ftime of year when pregnant ewes and
OL,18,Fnewborn lambs are vulnerable.
