OL,3,CFarmer recalls emotional and financial
OL,4,Ctoll of losing sheep in dog attacks
OL,6,FIt is an offence in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fto allow any dog on land with
OL,8,Flivestock on it.
OL,10,FAgriculture Minister Andrew Muir said:
OL,11,F"I am very aware that livestock
OL,12,Fworrying can have a devastating
OL,13,Fimpact, beyond the financial losses,
OL,14,Fcausing acute animal suffering and
OL,15,Fdistress on the farmer. In Northern
OL,16,FIreland, it is already a criminal
OL,17,Foffence under the Dogs (Northern
OL,18,FIreland) Order 1983 to allow a dog on
OL,19,Fany land containing livestock unless
OL,20,Fthe dog is under control.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
